name: Winsome Earle-Sears
tweet: BTW, if you aren't appointed to the Board of Education, that's one thing, because you still have your freedom. But when someone is in prison seeking parole, they need a board to hear their case. Freedom v. Board of Education. Again, don't play with people's freedom.

name: Winsome Earle-Sears
tweet: We should not play politics with people's lives. As someone who had a prison ministry, my heart goes out to those who have earned a second chance.
